      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SCANDALEYES (2) is a two-year-old filly by Art Major from Stunin Eyes Only on debut. A nice draw on the front line should ensure a cosy run. Looks to have some talent based on a recent trial win. Well-placed to score at her first appearance. FUNNY AS (7) finished a head from the winner in third at this track over 2185m last start at her first career run. Must overcome a very wide draw. Meets a comparable field so she can certainly take this out. MADE FOR ME (4) is looking to improve on her last-start third in a Listed contest won by Seaside Serenade over 1730m at Gloucester Park four months ago. Ideally drawn and is a serious threat while fresh. WOODBRIDGE ROSE (1) finished sixth last start at Listed level in a race won by Seaside Serenade over 1730m at Gloucester Park, beaten 19 metres. Drawn well so big run while fresh is on the cards.",
